Problem Statement:
Calculate the profit percentage using the columns 'budget' and 'revenue' and save the column as 'Profit_percentage'.
Return the columns 'original_title' and 'Profit_percentage'
Display all the movies and their percentage up to two decimals based on the new column created.

CODE:
select original_title,
round(((revenue-budget)/budget)*100,2) as Profit_percentage
from movies;
